{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act34side", "eventName": "生路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BP-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "不治的命運", "storyInfo": "西昆妲審訊襲擊研究所的深海教徒。深海獵人在手術完成後，離開城市。博士從烏爾比安口中得知當年斬殺伊莎瑪拉行動的更多真相。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g11_aegirroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1392_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海巡隊。你是來審問我的？", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“審問”，哈，我從沒想過這個詞居然會和自己有關。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在侵入研究所的時候就應該想到了。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之前呢？你我之間究竟有什麼區別？", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你在這裡“審問”，而我在這裡“受審”？", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有時候會覺得我們的手段太溫和了。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽伊比利亞的使節說，他們會在審問階段就應用刑罰。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒有更多廢話了，交代你的身分。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先前負責培育行道珊瑚。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作案動機？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有仔細觀察過路邊的行道珊瑚嗎，海巡隊？", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們希望每一條街道的每一株行道珊瑚，都呈現出不同的形態、色澤，並具備多樣化的功能。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬥智場東側的那一株，物流纜線從它滿是空洞的身軀間穿行，在纜線微光的映照下，一隻隻珊瑚蟲反射出點點明光……", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像是一片小小的星雲。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有港口樞紐外圍——", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在剛剛，我仔細觀察了不只一株行道珊瑚，在你們先前的試驗田。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位無辜的資料分析師就在那裡死去。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的理想，她的執念，她所喜愛的那些藻類……與你所描述的行道珊瑚一樣美。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你們謀害了她。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你問得很對。那你與她之間究竟有什麼差別？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你能活著，而她必須死去？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為她發現……", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發現了什麼？怎麼不說了？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，我應該把這個問題拿去問卡西婭？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海教會對航道計劃動了什麼手腳？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們集中攻擊的是信標，還是武器？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，深海教會，深海教徒。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是很不習慣被這麼稱呼，好陌生的名字。真不是你們海巡隊為了方便抓人才起的這些名字嗎？", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所謂教會、教徒，它的神聖性在哪裡？", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我甚至沒在崇拜什麼虛無縹緲的存在，我只是認同卡西婭的看法。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從瀰漫在阿戈爾的絕望當中，她看到了這個國家的脆弱性。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們太過看重事物的價值，卻又不肯承認這些價值是多麼脆弱而多變，他們變成了某種既定價值的忠實信徒。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可現在，這種價值正在崩塌。在阿戈爾完全陷入絕望之前，總有人得敲響警——", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*阿戈爾感嘆詞*！你在套我的話。", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會再說一個字了。你要是不耐煩，大可以解析我的腦波，反正也不費什麼力氣——", "name": "受傷的“研究員”"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提問是對你身為人的最後一點尊重，渣滓！", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以認為自己是無辜的，也可以認為自己的所作所為不屬於陰謀。但你終究會一點不漏地坦白所有細節。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，說。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g9_shipport", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$rebel_intro", "key": "$rebel_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二隊長。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂，離我們出發的時間很近了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道情況很緊急。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前線的軍力只能勉強與海嗣維持均勢，整整兩支艦隊完全覆滅的後果到現在完全顯現了出來。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照他們剛剛傳回的消息，第八、第十軍團幾次嘗試變陣都以失敗告終，他們陷入了苦戰。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果無法將信標投放到巢穴內的指定位置，繼續僵持……意味著航道計劃的失敗。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#9", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍團的艦隊即將不計代價地向海嗣發起全線進攻，吸引海嗣的注意力，至於我們——", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會切入戰場的死角，深入巢穴，投放信標。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。斯卡蒂，你覺得自己的狀態怎麼樣？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#5", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少剛才我睡得很好。自那場戰役以來，我還是第一次體驗無夢的睡眠。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在城內的局勢更加動盪……你知道博士去哪了嗎？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二隊長，我知道你提博士是想說什麼。你想讓我去維持秩序，保護博士……總之，你想讓我繼續留在城裡。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坦白地說，我在猶豫。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清掃海洋裡的渣滓是深海獵人的責任，但我也需要為你們的安全負責。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂，回到海洋後，伊莎瑪拉是否有醒轉的跡象？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果它在，那它很安靜。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果它說話，那我會讓它閉嘴。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二隊長，我找你其實有話要說。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之前做事從來不像現在這樣謹小慎微。我們有一套應對這種情況的做法。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果那些深海教徒的神，那些渣滓口中的“伊莎瑪拉”真的存在在我的身體裡，一旦我失控，那你就當場處決我，很簡單。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的心臟就在這裡，你不會失手。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂——", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒完，二隊長。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你，或者鯊魚，在戰鬥中比我先受到了那些渣滓的影響，我也不會手下留情。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂，我剛剛是想說，大戰在即，沒什麼能比這樣一番話更讓人欣慰了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們走。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞倫緹娜小姐。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小鳥，去掉那讓人難過的後綴吧，我們之間原來這麼生分嗎？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……勞倫緹娜。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來到阿戈爾的城市這麼久，我們竟然才第一次見面，真令人難過。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直想帶我們勇敢的戰士見識海洋深處真正的狩獵。偏偏這次我們要去的巢穴太遠、太深，沒辦法帶上你。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，就算不是這樣，我現在也應該留在彌利亞留姆。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段時間，城裡發生了一些事。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我第一次穿戴深潛裝置進入海洋，立刻就被海流沖得東倒西歪……我必須承認，這樣的我無法成為助力，只會成為拖累。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也不必這麼妄自菲薄。第一次總是艱難的。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，相比巢穴，我在城市裡能做的事更多。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等你們完成任務，阿戈爾的武器系統開始淨空這片海域時，我還需要盡快回到卡門閣下身邊，應對海面上的變化。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，原來你的意思是，我們還會再多分開一段時間。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本該給你們帶些餞別的禮物，可來到彌利亞留姆之前，我沒料到會有這種情況，沒能準備什麼……", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，我們還會再見的。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然這次不必把嗆得半死的你從海裡抱上來，但我覺得這次大戰後的重逢會以另一種方式刻骨銘心。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳！……斯卡蒂她們來了！", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞倫緹娜，你多小心。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們聊完了？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出發吧，獵人們。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g5_aegirstreet_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "看來你已經得到了你想要的證據。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line216"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，你的幫助很大。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那麼，結果是？;不打算將發現同步給我嗎？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line222", "option2": "line222"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先前提到，尚在城內的信標與已經投放進海嗣巢穴的信標之間，存在異常的訊息交流。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在來看，大部分操作都是在C-22研究所，也就是我們剛剛潛入的地方完成的。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不完全了解信標系統與第Ⅳ級武器的原理，但從這些訊息交流的內容依然能模糊地推斷出——", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信標與武器的聯動關係被改變了。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如我所想，航道計劃從高層被滲透了。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "“如我所想”。;你從一開始就對航道計劃抱有這樣的懷疑？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line232", "option2": "line232"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早在航道計劃誕生之前，我就已經對阿戈爾產生了懷疑。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這種懷疑從何而來？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line239"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那場決定性的戰役。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "原本是你向“初生”揮出致命一擊。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line245"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你卻在關鍵時刻與隊伍失去了聯繫。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line247"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "將斬殺“初生”的重負留給了斯卡蒂。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line249"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你已經知道了。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂比我預想中還要信任你。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "根據她的描述，不難推測當時的情形。;斯卡蒂其實並不清楚發生了什麼。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line256", "option2": "line256"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的失職是出於一瞬間的分神。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在最靠近伊莎瑪拉核心器官的那個洞窟，或者腔室，我發現了某樣本不應存在的東西。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "粗糙的肉質層，渾濁的黏液，我原本以為那只是它身體的某一處結節，直到我看清周邊的刻度和紋路……", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一個，鏽蝕的水脈儀。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": 